data.description: FHA LOAN IS ASSUMABLE TO QUALIFIED BUYER AT 2.875%. This 4 BDRM, 2.5 BATH, 2-story home is situated on a level, .25 acre cul-de-sac lot in the sought-after Plum Creek Community. The entrance leads past a Formal Dining Room & Office/Sitting Room to the open Living Room w/gas log fireplace & hardwood floors that were completely refinished in August 2020. The Kitchen has tiled floor, lovely granite counters, breakfast area & stainless steel appliances including Refrigerator. Primary Suite features a tray ceiling w/dual sinks, tile floor, garden tub, shower & walk-in closet in the Primary Bath. Gas water heater (2022). All new light fixtures on main (2022). French drain + moisture barrier in crawl space (2021). New carpet & shutters (2020). HVAC replaced (2017). New windows (2015). Roof (2012). Full sized 2-car garage plus a two-level deck that overlooks the roomy, fenced backyard. Home is a MUST SEE for anyone seeking to purchase in highly desirable Huntersville! Home Warranty at closing!
